{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Push a Block is a puzzle game where you need to arrange the blocks on stage to reach the end. You can only move the blocks by moving into them, but if there is another block behind it, or something else doesn't let you move it, you'll climb it</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/gif_new_complete_stage.gif?t=1739743542\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game has a very simple control, but will slowly start presenting new mechanics which will make you really have to think to reach the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/gif_new_lift_block.gif?t=1739743542\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress in the game new enviroments will appear, each presenting it's new mechanic that will add to the stages difficulty and complexity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/gif_new_slide_on_Ice.gif?t=1739743542\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2172350?t=1739743542","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2172350?t=1739743542","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/39b81c896ef442cdd0172b9bdd2a7a3003193e4a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739743542","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/39b81c896ef442cdd0172b9bdd2a7a3003193e4a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739743542","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"